text: Timashevsk, sometimes romanized Timashyovsk, is a town and the administrative center of Timashevsky District of Krasnodar Krai, Russia, located on the Kirpili River 73 kilometers north of Krasnodar, the administrative center of the krai. * Type: Town with 52,600 residents * Description: human settlement in Timashyovsky District, Krasnodar Krai, Russia * Also known as: Timashevsk, Timashyovskaya, TimashÃ«vsk, Timoschewskaja and Timoshevskaya
